Provider Network Management Enhancements

Use a new app to enable payers to seamlessly complete the recruiting, credentialing, and contracting processes in the provider management lifecycle. Integrate the Provider Network Management app with DocuSign to collect e-signatures from applicants and reCAPTCHA to ensure human interaction.

Enable payers to use the new Provider Network Management app within Health Cloud for seamless provider management.
Payers can obtain e-signatures on applications using Provider Network Management integrated with DocuSign.
Enhance security with reCAPTCHA in the Provider registration form.
title: Provider Network Management Enhancements in Salesforce
